dge%2C%20where%20he%20was%20attending%20events%20hosted%20by%20Harvard%20University%20and%20%3Cspan%3Eventure%20capital%20firm%20Xfund%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20the%20type%20of%20app%20he%20envisioned%20for%20future%20AI%20agents%20could%20live%20in%20the%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20futuristic%20app%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuper-competent%20colleague%20that%20knows%20absolutely%20everything%20about%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20every%20email%2C%20every%20conversation%20I've%20ever%20had%2C%20but%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20an%20extension.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Altman%20thinks%20AI%20devices%20are%20exciting%2C%20he%20told%20MIT%20Technology%20Review%20that%20consumer%20hardware%20for%20new%20technology%20was%20%26quot%3Bso%20far%26quot%3B%20from%20his%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20CEO%20has%20been%20rumored%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-head-iphone-designer-jony-ive-ai-device-openai-report-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsidering%20the%20development%20of%20his%20own%20AI%20device%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20The%20Information%20reported%20that%20Altman%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20Jony%20Ive%2C%20the%20designer%20of%20Apple's%20iPhone%2C%20about%20building%20a%20new%20AI%20hardware%20product.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Masayoshi%20Son%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20SoftBank%2C%20was%20also%20brought%20into%20their%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Inisder%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20AI%20hardware%20launches%20have%20been%20met%20with%20mixed%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumane's%20AI%20Pin%20was%20widely%20criticized%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mkbh-dtrashes-humane-ai-pin