e%20with%20investing%2C%20financial%20planners%20suggest%20trying%20index%20funds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planners-suggest-index-funds-start-investing-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaid%20non-client%20promotion%3A%20Affiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting-rating-methodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20investing%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sitting%20in%20an%20office%20looking%20at%20her%20phone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66315a5610dfcda409651592%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMake%20sure%20you%20understand%20what%20fees%20you'll%20pay%20with%20an%20index%20fund%20before%20investing.%3Cp%3EOscar%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInvesting%20can%20be%20intimidating%2C%20but%20index%20funds%20are%20an%20accessible%20way%20to%20get%20started.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20getting%20started%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20an%20emergency%20fund%20in%20place%20so%20you%20can%20invest%20long-term.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndex%20funds%20are%20generally%20low-cost%2C%20but%20make%20sure%20you%20understand%20what%20fees%20are%20involved.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20new%20and%20experienced%20investors%20alike%2C%20it%20can%20be%20stressful%20to%20choose%20which%20stocks%20to%20buy%20with%20your%20hard-earned%20money.%20But%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20predict%20which%20stock%20will%20be%20the%20next%20to%20take%20off%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20likely%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20experts%20say%20to%20consider%20total%20stock%20market%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-invest-in-index-funds%5C%22%3Eindex%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20give%20you%20exposure%20to%20the%20stock%20market%20more%20broadly.%20These%20funds%20include%20companies%20you%20know%20and%20use%20every%20day%2C%20like%20Apple%20and%20Starbucks%2C%20but%20they%20also%20invest%20in%20smaller%20companies%20you've%20likely%20never%20heard%20of%20from%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20sectors%20(think%20healthcare%2C%20industrials%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20technology).%20These%20funds%20track%20a%20market%20index%2C%20such%20as%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20nice%2C%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20exposure%20to%20basically%20everything%20that's%20out%20there%20in%20the%20U.S.%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bryan%20Hasling%2C%20financial%20planner%20at%20Modern%20Financial%20Planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuild%20an%20emergency%20fund%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20index%20funds%20are%20still%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20investing%20goes%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20trade-offs%20to%20getting%20those%20long-term%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasling%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20something%20you%20should%20do%20with%20money%20you%20might%20need%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20start%20investing%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20financial%20advisors%20generally%20say%20should%20be%20at%20least%20enough%20to%20cover%20three%20to%20six%20months%20of%20your%20expenses)%20as%20well%20as%20money%20saved%20for%20any%20short-term%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20invest%20money%20you%20may%20need%20within%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20there's%20a%20chance%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20sell%20when%20the%20market%20is%20experiencing%20a%20short-term%20correction%2C%20Hasling%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20worth%20it%20if%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20let%20the%20money%20work%20over%20time%20through%20different%20cycles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20have%20several%20choices%20for%20brokerage%20and%20investment%20apps%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20investing%20in%20a%20total%20market%20index%20fund%20is%20as%20easy%20as%20buying%20a%20stock%20via%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%3Eonline%20brokerage%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcharles-schwab-brokerage-account-review%5C%22%3ECharles%20Schwab%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffidelity-investments-review%5C%22%3EFidelity%20Investments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-the-best-investment-apps%5C%22%3Einvestment%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frobinhood-investing-review%5C%22%3ERobinhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20(though%20you%20can%20also%20buy%20a%20fund%20from%20the%20fund%20company%20directly%20if%20you%20prefer).%20You%20can%20buy%20a%20full%20share%20of%20a%20fund%20or%20a%20fraction%20of%20a%20share%2C%20often%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%241.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20picking%20your%20total%20market%20index%20fund%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20many%20of%20the%20funds%20are%20tracking%20the%20same%20indexes.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20choice%20will%20ultimately%20come%20down%20to%20how%20much%20those%20funds%20cost.%20Check%20a%20fund's%20expense%20ratio%2C%20which%20is%20the%20fee%20associated%20with%20the%20overhead%20costs%20of%20the%20fund%20and%20is%20represented%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20your%20investment.%20Because%20these%20funds%20are%20passively%20managed%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20there%20isn't%20a%20Wall%20Street%20professional%20choosing%20which%20securities%20to%20buy%20or%20sell%20%E2%80%94%20the%20expense%20ratios%20are%20typically%20below%200.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIndex%20funds%20diversify%20your%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETotal%20stock%20market%20index%20funds%20may%20make%20sense%20to%20include%20in%20any%20investor's%20portfolio%2C%20but%20they%20can%20especially%20be%20good%20for%20new%20investors%20as%20they're%20an%20easy%20and%20inexpensive%20way%20to%20diversify%20your%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESusan%20Dziubinski%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20an%20investment%20specialist%20at%20investment%20research%20firm%20Morningstar%2C%20identified%20total%20market%20funds%20as%20one%20of%20the%20five%20best%20ways%20to%20invest%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20funds%20hold%20appeal%20for%20a%20few%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20Dziubinski%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BFor%20starters%2C%20index%20funds%20tend%20to%20be%20low%20cost%3B%20they%20also%20don't%20carry%20any%20key-person%20risk%20because%20index%20fund%20managers%20aren't%20actively%20picking%20stocks%20or%20bonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20total%20market%20funds%20offer%20significant%20diversification%20by%20investing%20very%20broadly.%20That%20diversification%20is%20key%20since%20it%20means%20that%20if%20some%20stocks%20in%20the%20fund%20tank%2C%20others%20may%20hold%20steady%20or%20even%20gain%20in%20value.%20The%20risk%20associated%20with%20investing%20in%20a%20total%20market%20fund%20is%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20risk%20associated%20with%20choosing%20a%20few%20stocks%20and%20hoping%20they%20soar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20funds%20can%20also%20%26quot%3Bbe%20great%20choices%20for%20investors%20as%20stand-alone%20investments%20or%20in%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20Dziubinski%20wrote.%20She%20says%20that%20while%20a%20young%20investor%20may%20opt%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20total%20U.S.%20stock%20market%20fund%20or%20total%20world%20stock%20fund%20(which%20includes%20stocks%20from%20around%20the%20globe)%2C%20that%20investor%20may%20want%20to%20add%20a%20total%20bond%20market%20fund%20to%20their%20portfolio%20as%20they%20get%20closer%20to%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planners-suggest-index-funds-start-investing-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714653961000%