-other-of-leaking-videos-5556892%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Prajwal%20Revanna's%20Ex%20Driver%2C%20BJP%20Leader%20Accuse%20Each%20Other%20Of%20Leaking%20Videos%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prevalence%20of%20such%20cases%2C%20including%20charges%20like%20assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20outrage%20modesty%2C%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20parties%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20It's%20alarming%20how%20candidates%20with%20criminal%20cases%20against%20them%20manage%20to%20win%20elections.%20This%20has%20been%20an%20ugly%20reality%20that%20no%20one%20has%20taken%20pains%20to%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20crucial%20demographic%20in%20elections%2C%20often%20considered%20%26quot%3Bkingmakers%26quot%3B%20and%20demonstrating%20higher%20turnout%20than%20men%20in%20many%20instances.%20However%2C%20incidents%20like%20these%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20episode%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20disillusionment%20among%20women%20voters%2C%20affecting%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritising%20Women%2C%20In%20Spirit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20despite%20the%20heavy%20rhetoric%20over%20women's%20representation%2C%20parties%20have%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20even%20half%20of%20the%20promised%2033%25%20quota%20for%20women%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fielding%20candidates.%20This%20may%20negatively%20impact%20women's%20perception%20of%20politics%20and%20politicians%20at%20a%20time%20when%20their%20participation%20is%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliament%20must%20enact%20stricter%20laws%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20should%20implement%20more%20stringent%20rules%20for%20candidate%20information%2C%20especially%20regarding%20criminal%20cases%2C%20to%20empower%20voters%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%20Parties%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20need%20to%20prioritise%20genuine%20concerns%20and%20respect%20for%20women's%20welfare%20over%20political%20gains%20and%20superficial