and%20lifestyle%20governs%20how%20long%20they'll%20live%2C%20but%20a%20study%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Febm.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2Febmed%2Fearly%2F2024%2F04%2F16%2Fbmjebm-2023-112583.full.pdf%3Fwith-ds%3Dyes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBMJ%20Evidence-Based%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20compare%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20two%20on%20lifespan.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20looked%20at%20data%20from%20353%2C742%20adults%20with%20European%20ancestry%20collected%20between%202006%20and%202010%2C%20and%20tracked%20their%20health%20until%202021%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-centenarian-longevity-tips-met-superagers-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenes%20or%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20bigger%20impact%20on%20their%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20ranked%20the%20participants%20according%20to%20whether%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fis-obesity-genetic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenetically%20predisposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20diseases%20that%20could%20shorten%20their%20lifespan%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20led%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle.%20Not%20smoking%2C%20exercising%20regularly%2C%20eating%20a%20healthy%20diet%2C%20getting%20enough%20sleep%2C%20having%20a%20healthy%20body%20shape%2C%20and%20drinking%20alcohol%20in%20moderation%20defined%20a%20favorable%20lifestyle%2C%20while%20the%20opposite%20was%20unfavorable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHealthy%20lifestyle%20choices%20appeared%20to%20offset%20the%20impact%20of%20genes%20on%20longevity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20who%20led%20%26quot%3Bunfavorable%26quot%3B%20lifestyles%20were%2078%25%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20early%20than%20people%20with%20favorable%20lifestyles%20%E2%80%94%20regardless%20of%20whether%20they%20had%20genes%20linked%20to%20a%20shorter%20or%20longer%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20those%20who%20were%20genetically%20predisposed%20to%20short%20lifespans%20were%2021%25%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20early%20than%20those%20predisposed%20to%20longer%20lives%2C%20even%20if%20they%20made%20favorable%20lifestyle%20choices.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20appeared%20to%20offset%20the%20effects%20of%20genes%20linked%20to%20a%20shorter%20lifespan%20by%2062%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20favorable%20lifestyle%20choices%20despite%20having%20genes%20linked%20to%20a%20shorter%20lifespan%20was%20linked%20to%20living%205.22%20years%20longer%20than%20those%20who%20made%20unfavorable%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Liz%20Williams%2C%20a%20lecturer%20in%20human%20nutrition%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Healthy%20Lifespan%20Institute%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Sheffield%2C%20who%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20wasn't%20surprised%20that%20the%20study%20found%20a%20link%20between%20lifespan%2C%20genes%2C%20and%20lifestyle%20factors.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20effects%20of%20lifestyle%20factors%20in%20the%20study%20were%20notable%20because%20they%20suggest%20that%20while%20we%20can't%20change%20our%20genes%2C%20healthy%20habits%20may%20lessen%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENot%20smoking%2C%20exercising%20regularly%2C%20getting%20enough%20sleep%2C%20and%20eating%20a%20healthy%20diet%20could%20help%20you%20live%20longer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20argued%20that%20not%20smoking%2C%20exercising%20regularly%2C%20sleeping%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20a%20night%2C%20and%20eating%20a%20healthy%20diet%20formed%20what%20they%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Boptimal%20lifestyle%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20appeared%20to%20help%20people%20live%20longer%20while%20being%20sustainable%20over%20a%20long%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20defined%20adequate%20exercise%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Heart%20Association's%20guidelines%20of%20150%20minutes%20of%20moderate%20activity%2C%20such%20as%20walking%2C%20gardening%2C%20or%20tennis%2C%20or%2075%20minutes%20of%20vigorous%20activity%20a%20week%2C%20such%20as%20hiking%2C%20swimming%2C%20or%20heavy%20yard%20work.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fmediterranean-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20balanced%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20adequate%20amount%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20fish%2C%20and%20a%20low%20amount%20of%20red%20and%20processed%20meats%20was%20deemed%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20didn't%20include%20having%20a%20healthy%20body%20shape%20%E2%80%94%20i.e.%2C%20having%20a%20BMI%20of%20between%2018.5%20and%2030%20%E2%80%94%20or%20reducing%20alcohol%20consumption%20in%20their%20%26quot%3Boptimal%20lifestyle%20combination.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20the%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20states%20that%20obesity%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%2C%20and%20that%20drinking%20too%20much%20alcohol%20can%20shorten%20people's%20lives%20by%20an%20average%20of%2024%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20said%20that%20alcohol%20consumption%20and%20body%20shape%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20still%20matter%26quot%3B%20for%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20study%20was%20observational%2C%20meaning%20the%20researchers%20couldn't%20prove%20that%20the%20lifestyle%20changes%20improved%20the%20participants'%20longevity.%20Plus%2C%20because%20this%20study%20was%20only%20done%20on%20people%20of%20European%20descent%2C%20the%20same%20associations%20might%20not%20apply%20to%20other%20populations%2C%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-lifestyle-changes-live-longer-healthy-habits-genes-study-2024-5%5C%22%3