off%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Congress'%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20is%20heard%20saying%20%26quot%3Bit's%20better%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20than%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20TMC%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20eight-second%20video%20clip%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Bengal's%20Murshidabad%20on%20Tuesday.%20NDTV%20cannot%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20was%20quick%20to%20label%20the%20video%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Congress'%20comm%20boss%2C%20said%20the%20goal%20of%20his%20party%20is%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%2C%20underscoring%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20parties%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20in%20alliance%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20know%20the%20context%20of%20what%20Adhir%20ji%20said%2C%20but%20we%20aim%20to%20reduce%20the%20numbers%20of%20BJP%20in%20West%20Bengal%20significantly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20won%2018%20out%20of%2042%20seats%2C%20we%20have%20to%20reduce%20their%20numbers%20and%20that%20is%20the%20only%20goal.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20assembly%20election%2C%20this%20is%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Congress%2C%20along%20with%20Left%20parties%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20TMC%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20said%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20though%20we%20are%20not%20in%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20holds%20Mr%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20%C2%A0breakdown%20of%20seat-sharing%20discussions%20with%20Congress%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20said%20after%20acting%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Beyes%20and%20ears%20of%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20has%20now%20been%20promoted%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BListen%20to%20how%20the%20B-Team%20member%20is%20openly%20asking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20-%20a%20party%20that%20refused%20to%20release%20Bengal's%20rightful%20dues%20and%20deprived%20our%20people%20of%20their%20rights.%20Only%20a%20Bangla-Birodhi%20can%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20repeatedly%20insulted%20Bengal's%20icons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20No.%202%20in%20the%20party%2C%20accused%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Bengal%20Congress%20chief%2C%20of%20being%20an%20agent%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20held%20him%20responsible%20for%20obstructing%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20wanted%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20happen%20in%20Bengal.%20But%20Chowdhury%20prevented%20it%20to%20strengthen%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Trinamool%20general%20secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20The%20Trinamool%20won%2022%20out%20of%2042%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20BJP%2017%2C%20and%20Congress%20got%20two%20seats.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714647000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc3ief52k_mamata-banerjee-ani_625x300_02_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjees-answer-to-congress-leaders-vote-for-bjp-clip-5572161%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader's%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20to%20vote%20for%20