ekhar%20Suman%2C%20who%20marked%20his%20acting%20debut%20with%20the%201984%20film%20%3Ci%3EUtsav%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20shared%20an%20interesting%20anecdote%20about%20working%20with%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20who%20was%20a%20newcomer%20back%20then.%20The%20actor%20shared%20that%20he%20used%20to%20pick%20up%20Madhuri%20Dixit%20on%20a%20bike%20when%20they%20started%20working%20together.%20Shekhar%20Suman%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EUtsav%3C%2Fi%3E%20had%20gotten%20delayed%20and%20in%20between%20that%20and%20%3Cem%3EAnubhav%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20day%20I%20got%20a%20call%20where%20a%20director%20wanted%20to%20sign%20me%20for%20a%20film%20called%3Cem%3E%20Maanav%20Hatya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20I%20played%20a%20true%20journalist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fadhyayan-and-dad-shekhar-suman-attend-heeramandi-screening-in-a-ferrari-5520586%5C%22%3EShekhar%20Suman%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20director%20said%20%E2%80%98Paise%20bade%20kam%20hain%20isme.%20(I%20don't%20have%20money)'%20He%20only%20offered%20me%20Rs%205%2C000.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20signed%20%3Cem%3EUtsav%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Rs%2025%2C000%20and%20was%20given%20Rs%2010%2C000%20as%20the%20signing%20amount.%20When%20he%20offered%20me%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20this%20one%2C%20I%20was%20a%20little%20disappointed%20and%20there%20was%20no%20heroine%20also.%20He%20told%20me%20it%20was%20a%20new%20heroine%20named%20Madhuri%20Dixit.%20I%20asked%20him%20to%20make%20me%20meet%20her.%20When%20he%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20would%20do%20it%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20do%20that%20film.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShekhar%20Suman%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20of%20course%20I'll%20do%20it.%20I%20justified%20that%20if%20Rekhaji%20could%20work%20with%20me%20%E2%80%93%20a%20newcomer%2C%20then%20me%20being%20a%20newcomer%20why%20won't%20I%20work%20with%20another%20newcomer%3F%20We%20went%20and%20met%20Madhuri%20at%20her%20house.%20She%20took%20some%20time%20to%20come%20out.%20When%20I%20saw%20her%20she%20was%20resplendent%20and%20looked%20glorious%20and%20pretty.%20I%20told%20the%20director%20that%20your%20film%20is%20about%20to%20start.%20And%20I%20will%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20second%20film%20for%20both%20of%20us%20individually%2C%20and%20producer%20aake%20kehta%20hai%2C%20%3Ci%3E%E2%80%98location%20ke%20paise%20nahi%20hain%2C%20aapka%20ghar%20milega%20to%20shoot%3F'%20Maine%20kaha%2C%20%E2%80%98arey%20bhai%2C%20aisa%20karo.%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3EThodi%20dino%20mein%20tum%20mujhse%20paise%20lelo%20and%20shoot%20karna.%20Ghar%20bhi%20lelo%2C%20kapde%20bhi%20lelo%2C%20motorcycle%20bhi%20lelo.%20Joh%20karna%20hai%20karlo%2C%20joh%20lena%20hai%20leno.%3C%2Fi%3E'%20%3Ci%3EToh%20woh%20bola%2C%20%E2%80%98dhekho%2C%20abhi%20Madhuri%20ko%20aane%20ke%20liye%20taxi%20ke%20paise%20nahi%20hai%20toh%20can%20you%20go%20pick%20her%20up%3F'%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(The%20producers%20said%20that%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20budget%20for%20a%20location%20and%20requested%20to%20use%20my%20house.%20I%20said%20take%20money%20from%20me%20to%20shoot.%20Take%20my%20house%2C%20clothes%2C%20bike%20%E2%80%93%20whatever%20you%20want.%20Then%20the%20producers%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20could%20go%20and%20pick%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20as%20she%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20to%20come%20to%20the%20shoot%20location).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20a%20nice%20laugh%20about%20it%2C%20the%20actor%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EToh%20main%20Madhuri%20Dixit%20ko%20motorcycle%20pe%20lene%20jaata%20tha.%20Phir%20bola%20makeup%20man%20ke%20paise%20nahi%20hain%E2%80%A6%20toh%20mere%20ko%20bola%20ki%20meri%20wife%2C%20Alka%2C%20ko%20bolo%20ki%20wo%20aachi%20lagti%20hai%20toh%20woh%20makeup%20kar%20degi.%20Toh%20Alka%20used%20to%20do%20Madhuri%20Dixit's%20makeup.%20Kapde%20bhi%20chhaiye%20the.%20Alka%20used%20to%20give%20her%20clothes%20also.%20%3C%2Fi%3EPoor%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20she%20was%20such%20a%20sweet%2C%20naive%2C%20Maharashtrian%20girl%20%E2%80%A6%20%3Cem%3Ejoh%20bolte%20thay%20(producers)%20woh%20karti%20thi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20used%20to%20drop%20her%20off%20after%20shoots%20and%20take%20her%20to%20dance%20practices%20also.%20(So%20I%20went%20and%20picked%20her%20up%20by%20bike.%20They%20then%20didn't%20have%20money%20for%20a%20makeup%20artist%2C%20so%20they%20requested%20my%20wife%2C%20Alka%2C%20to%20do%20the%20makeup.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Alka%20even%20lent%20Madhuri%20clothes%20for%20the%20movie.%20Madhuri%20was%20so%20naive%2C%20she%20did%20everything%20she%20was%20told%20to.)%20The%20film%20somehow%20got%20completed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShekhar%20Suman%20said%20that%20in%20his%20third%20film%20%3Ci%3EAnubhav%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20he%20was%20supposed%20to%20share%20screen%20space%20with%20Madhuri%20Dixit.%20But%20she%20was%20replaced%20by%20Padmini%20Kolhapure.%20The%20actor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20third%20film%20%3Ci%3EAnubhav%3C%2Fi%3E%20also%20had%20Madhuri%20cast%20in%20it%2C%20but%20two%20days%20later%2C%20she%20was%20replaced%20by%20Padmini%20Kolhapure%2C%20who%20was%20a%20much%20bigger%20star%20then.%20That%20film%20became%20a%20huge%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714646760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fklnm41p8_vicky-_625x300_02_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshekhar-suman-recalls-picking-up-madhuri-dixit-for-shoot-on-his-bike-5571908%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shekhar%20Suman%2C%20who%20marked%20his%20acting%20debut%20with%20the%201984%20film%20Utsav%2C%20shared%20an%20interesting%20anecdote%20about%20working%20with%20Madhuri%20Dixit%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshekhar-suman-recalls-picking-up-madhuri-dixit-for-shoot-on-his-bike-5571908%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainme