rty-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhatever%20the%20Houseparty%20app%20was%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-and-fall-of-clubhouse-poster-child-pandemic-hype-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClubhouse%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Chill%20time%2C%20for%20good%20reason%2C%20required%20work%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20life%20has%20become%20much%20more%20normal%20for%20many%20people.%20They're%20back%20in%20the%20office%2C%20going%20to%20restaurants%20and%20live%20events%2C%20gathering%20with%20friends%20and%20family%20in%20person.%20Some%20of%20the%20structured%20nature%20of%20their%20social%20interactions%2C%20however%2C%20have%20not%20reverted%20to%20their%20previous%20form.%20The%20stilted%20nature%20of%20some%20pandemic-era%20habits%20%E2%80%94%20many%20that%20come%20with%20a%20dash%20of%20work%20%E2%80%94%20stuck%20around%20as%20a%20permanent%20feature.%20Case%20in%20point%3A%20the%20PowerPoint%20party%2C%20where%20people%20get%20together%20to%20show%20each%20other%20presentations%20on%20various%20topics%20in%20the%20name%20of%20having%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowerPoint%20parties%20supposedly%20started%20in%202012%20as%20%26quot%3Bdrink%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20learn%26quot%3B%20gatherings%20in%20Canada.%20Over%20time%2C%20they%20spread.%20Kids%20at%20Harvard%20were%20doing%20them%20in%202018%20because%2C%20come%20on%2C%20it's%20Harvard%20kids.%20Of%20course%2C%20they%20were.%20When%20COVID-19%20hit%2C%20they%20really%20took%20off%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youngs.%20It%20made%20some%20sense%20during%20the%20period%20when%20we%20were%20trapped%20inside.%20It's%20easy%20enough%20to%20share%20your%20screen%20on%20Zoom%20or%20Google%20Meet%2C%20and%20it%20was%20better%20to%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20activity%20to%20do%20instead%20of%20just%20staring%20at%20people's%20faces%20(and%20your%20own)%20for%20the%20eighth%20day%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20we've%20gotten%20back%20to%20normal%20hangouts%2C%20people%20are%20still%20connecting%20their%20laptops%20to%20TVs%20and%20sharing%20slides%20in%20social%20settings.%20Take%20a%20spin%20around%20TikTok%2C%20and%20you%20can%20find%20loads%20of%20PowerPoint-party%20content.%20There%20are%20presentations%20on%20which%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20songs%20best%20represent%20each%20friend%2C%20what%20to%20do%20if%20you're%20trapped%20in%20an%20elevator%2C%20or%20whether%20pigeons%20are%20a%20pest%20or%20a%20pet.%20In%20March%2C%20Cosmopolitan%20put%20out%20a%20list%20of%2055%20PowerPoint%20ideas%20to%20%26quot%3Bspice%20up%20your%20next%20at-home%20hang%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20included%20ideas%20such%20as%20making%20a%20pitch%20for%20each%20of%20your%20friends'%20celebrity%20look-alike%20or%20%26quot%3Branking%20cartoon%20characters%20by%20hotness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20guess%20I%20can%20see%20how%20this%20might%20be%20enjoyable%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20presentations%20do%20seem%20genuinely%20clever%20and%20funny%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20man.%20I%20love%20my%20friends%2C%20and%20also%20I%20absolutely%20do%20not%20want%20to%20do%20this%20with%20any%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20a%20PowerPoint%20night%20is%20not%20that%20far%20off%20from%2C%20say%2C%20a%20game%20or%20movie%20night.%20It's%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20creative%20and%20turn%20something%20you%20do%20at%20work%20into%20something%20silly%20and%20social.%20But%20also%2C%20%3Cem%3Emust%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20turn%20something%20we%20do%20at%20work%20into%20something%20we%20do%20in%20our%20personal%20lives%3F%20Just%20hanging%20out%20without%20a%20plan%20is%20fine%20and%20pleasant.%20Spontaneity%20is%20exciting!%20Another%20way%20to%20be%20creative%20is%20to%20put%20yourself%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20you%20have%20to%20be%20creative%20by%20thinking%20on%20your%20feet%20about%20conversation%20topics%20and%20activities%20at%20random.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20PowerPoint%20party%20also%20%3Ca