ime%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20poll%20rally%20in%20Gujarat's%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20stressed%20that%20no%20Congress%20leader%20had%20opposed%20the%20statement%20yet.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20tacit%20understanding.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20INDI%20alliance%20is%20trying%20to%20divide%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20OBC%20and%20general%20categories%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20they%20are%20raising%20the%20slogan%20of%20Vote%20Jihad.%20This%20shows%20how%20dangerous%20their%20intentions%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20counter%20comes%20days%20after%20Maria%20Alam%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Farrukhabad%2C%20appealed%20to%20Muslim%20voters%20to%20launch%20a%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B.%20A%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%2C%20she%20was%20campaigning%20for%20party%20candidate%20Naval%20Kishore%20Shakya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20remove%20this%20government.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20the%20Constitution%20and%20democracy%20are%20under%20threat.%20But%20I%20say%20that%20insaniyat%20(humanity)%20is%20under%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Maria%20Alam%20for%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20classes%2C%20among%20other%20sections%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act.%20A%20case%20has%20also%20been%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Khurshid%2C%20who%20was%20chief%20guest%20at%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20niece's%20statement%2C%20the%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20avoids%20certain%20words%20in%20public%20addresses%20because%20they%20are%20misinterpreted.%20%26quot%3BJihad%20means%20to%20fight%20against%20a%20situation.%20Her%20intention%20must%20have%20been%20to%20carry%20out%20vote%20jihad%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Vikas%20Kumar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20video%20of%20Maria%20Alam%20Khan%2C%20an%20SP%20leader%2C%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20she%20is%20seen%20asking%20for%20votes%20on%20religious%20grounds.%20This%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Farrukhabad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20being%20contested%20by%20Samajwadi%20Party%20as%20part%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20seat%2C%20represented%20by%20Mr%20Khurshid%20twice%2C%20is%20currently%20held%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Sitting%20MP%20Mukesh%20Rajput%2C%20who%20won%20it%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20polls%2C%20has%20been%20given%20another%20chance.%20Polling%20in%20Farrukhabad%20is%20due%20on%20May%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20today%20alleged%20that%20the%20Opposition%20party%20is%20in%20a%20partnership%20with%20Pakistan.%20%26quot%3BThe%20weak%20Congress%20government%20used%20to%20give%20dossiers%20to%20the%20masters%20of%20terror.%20But%2C%20Modi's%20strong%20government%20kills%20terrorists%20on%20their%20ground.%20It%20is%20a%20coincidence%2C%20today%20Congress%20is%20getting%20weaker%20in%20India.%20Congress%20is%20dying%20here%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20crying.%20Now%20Pakistani%20leaders%20are%20offering%20'dua'%20for%20Congress.%20Pakistan%20is%20eager%20to%20make%20'shehzaada'%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20already%20Pakistan's%20fan.%20This%20partnership%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20Congress%20has%20now%20been%20completely%20exposed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20came%20after%20former%20Pakistan%20minister%C2%A0Chaudhry%20Fawad%20Hussain%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BRahul%20on%20fire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714642920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F83udku28_modi-anand_625x300_02_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-maria-alam-pm-modi-says-up-leaders-vote-jihad-remark-exposed-india-bloc-strategy-5571334%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latching%20on%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bvote%20jihad%26quot%3B%20remark%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Salman%20Khurshid's%20niece%20Maria%20Alam%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20leader%20had%20%26quot%3Bexposed%26quot%3B%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20strategy%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-maria-alam-pm-modi-says-up-leaders-vote-jihad-remark-exposed-india-bloc-strategy-5571334%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-maria-alam-pm-modi-says-up-leaders-vote-jihad-remark-exposed-india-bloc-strategy-5571334%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-maria-alam-pm-modi-says-up-leaders-vote-jihad-remark-exposed-india-bloc-strategy-5571334%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivo%20V30e%20smartphone%20with%205500%20mAh%20battery%20launched%20in%20India%3A%20Price%2C%20specs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714642848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1714642042-0891.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-v30e-smartphone-with-5500-mah-battery-launched-in-india-price-specs-124050200607_1.html%2