%20match%20against%20Ireland%20in%202023.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20played%2015%20matches%20in%20the%20format%20scoring%20356%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20176.24.%20The%20southpaw%20played%20his%20last%20T20I%20match%20for%20India%20in%20January%202024%2C%20against%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20Rohan%20Gavaskar%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20selection%20committee's%20decision%20of%20dropping%20Rinku%2C%20while%20another%20ex-India%20player%20Virender%20Sehwag%20tried%20to%20understand%20the%20rationale%20behind%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20IPL%202024%20is%20the%20metric%2C%20where%20has%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20picked%20wickets%20for%20RCB%3F%20Suryakumar%20Yadav...%20he%20was%20always%20in%20my%20team%2C%20and%20he%20should%20be%20there%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%20too.%20But%20even%20he%20hasn't%20performed%20(for%20MI)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohan%20Gavaskar%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnaExLCL3B24%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20players%20are%20going%20there%20on%20reputation.%20Like%20Suryakumar%2C%20his%20reputation%20is%20that%20he%20is%20an%20explosive%20hitter.%20Yes%2C%20he%20can%20have%20bad%20days.%20Rinku%20Singh%20is%20also%20like%20him%2C%20the%20difference%20is%20that%20he%20is%20young%20and%20Suryakumar%20is%20experienced.%20And%20Indian%20selectors%20have%20preferred%20experience.%20Rinku%20is%20young%2C%20he%20can%20play%20later%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Virender%20Sehwag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20said%20after%20the%20previous%20World%20Cup%20that%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20won't%20play%20in%202024%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20I'm%20sure%20they%20won't%20play%20the%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sehwag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20squad%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(Captain)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(Vice%20Captain)%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C