es.%20Growing%20vegetables%20was%20merely%20a%20fun%20hobby%20for%20the%20Chennai%20resident%20until%202016%20when%20he%20became%20a%20physiotherapy%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20several%20patients%20who%20complained%20of%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%20The%20underlying%20cause%20of%20such%20rising%20issues%20is%20the%20consumption%20of%20adulterated%20food%20that%20is%20prepared%20using%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Naveen%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20market%20is%20flooded%20with%20genetically%20modified%20seeds%20which%20negatively%20affect%20human%20health.%20There%20have%20been%20concerns%20that%20the%20food%20prepared%20using%20such%20seeds%20has%20carcinogenic%20properties%20and%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20development%20of%20cancer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202016%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20was%20eager%20to%20encourage%20residents%20to%20take%20up%20organic%20farming%20at%20home.%20In%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20has%20transformed%20his%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace%20into%20a%20green%20haven.%20Using%20his%20%3Cem%3Ethatha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(grandfather)%20best%20gardening%20secrets%2C%20he%20currently%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20%E2%80%94%20including%20spinach%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20brinjals%2C%20custard%20apple%2C%20lemons%2C%20mulberries%2C%20and%20dragon%20fruits%20in%20a%20small%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FChennai-dr-naveen-1-1714627454.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Using%20his%20grandpa's%20gardening%20secrets%2C%20Dr%20Naveen%20grows%20more%20than%20250%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2